        {
            "title": "澳門3月份博彩毛收入按升15%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">澳門監察協調局統計顯示，今年3月份澳門幸運博彩毛收入達226.12億澳門元，按年增長15%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source_licensed_Macau-gaming_shutterstock-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source_licensed_Macau-gaming_shutterstock-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今年首3個月，澳門幸運博彩毛收入合共658.73億澳門元，較去年同期的576.57億澳門元提升14.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15822990-%e6%be%b3%e9%96%803%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%bd%e5%8d%9a%e5%bd%a9%e6%af%9b%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e6%8c%89%e5%8d%8715",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250604_FI_source_licensed_Macau-gaming_shutterstock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 13:24:13",
